2. Results
2.1. GC/MS Analysis
GC/MS analysis of chloroform extracts from WT plants allowed the detection of most of the
components of the spike lavender essential oil [
] including monoterpenes, sesquiterpenes and,
at longer retention times, over 21 min, coumarin, as previously reported [
] (data not shown).
